Package: pio
Type: Package
Title: pio - Pretty I/O
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giulio Caravagna
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gcaravagn@gmail.com")
Description: `pio` is a package to print nice coloured outputs to the console. If you work with 
  R scripts that generate several loads or outputs, or if you just like to organize in a tidy 
  way on-screen outputs of your computations, then `pio`'s pretty I/O system is the package 
  that you are looking for.
